# Project Overview

This is a Next.js project built with TypeScript. It uses `tailwindcss` for styling and `react-aria-components` for accessible UI components.

## Key Files & Directories

- **`package.json`**: [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Defines project dependencies and scripts. Managed by PNPM ([pnpm-lock.yaml](mdc:pnpm-lock.yaml)).
- **`next.config.ts`**: [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts) - Configuration file for the Next.js framework.
- **`tsconfig.json`**: [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript compiler options.
- **`src/`**: [src](mdc:src) - Contains the main source code for the application (pages, components, etc.).
- **`Dockerfile`**: [Dockerfile](mdc:Dockerfile) & `docker-compose.yml`: [docker-compose.yml](mdc:docker-compose.yml) - Configuration for building and running the application with Docker.
- **Configuration Files**: Various configuration files for linting (`eslint.config.js`, `stylelint.config.js`), formatting (`prettier.config.js`), commit linting (`commitlint.config.ts`), etc. are present in the root directory.
